text: Matches was a global luxury e-commerce platform that sells ready-to-wear, shoes, bags and accessories for womenswear, menswear and lifestyle products. It has three stores in London, England. In July 2024, Matches closed after Frasers Group shut it down.Frasers Group to shut down Matches after two months MADELEINE SCHULZ, Vogue Business, March 7, 2024 ==References== Category:E-commerce
title: Matches Fashion
